      • getAirLevel

        @JvmStatic
public static int getAirLevel()

        Gets the player's air level.

        The returned value will be an integer. If the player is not taking damage, it will be between 300 (not in water) and 0. If the player is taking damage, it will be between -20 and 0, getting reset to 0 every time the player takes damage.

        Returns:
        the player's air level
